                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9824" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1486</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1737 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">数据资产入表赋能企业数字化转型——以开普云为例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Data asset inclusion empowers enterprise digital transformation - taking Cape Cloud as an example</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">管军，刘冬雪</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">河北工程大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">开普云信息科技股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">科研、咨询业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">5 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">数据资产；确认与计量；数字化转型；微案例none</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Data Assets; Confirmation and Measurement; Digital Transformation; Mini-case</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023年8月，财政部发布《企业数据资源相关会计处理暂行规定》要求后，各个公司分别对各自数据资产进行确认与计量，并及时披露。本案例以开普云信息科技股份有限公司为研究对象，作为数据密集型企业，其在经营过程中积累了海量数据。数据资产已经成为开普云的重要资产，在企业发展中凸显重要作用，而且开普云是第一家以外购数据资产入表的上市公司，成为数据资产入表的首批实践者。数据资产入表是企业数字化转型的重要组成部分，也是企业数字化转型的重要推动力。本案例旨在帮助学生了解数据资产的定义、类型以及外购数据资产如何入表及如何赋能企业数字化转型，引导学生学会在现有准则制度下对数据资产进行确认和计量，启发学生思考数据资产入表的意义，并以此为公司以外购数据资产入表提供借鉴。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">After the Ministry of Finance issued the &quot;Interim Provisions on Accounting Treatments Related to Enterprise Data Resources&quot; in August 2023, various companies respectively carried out the confirmation and measurement of their own data assets and disclosed them in a timely manner.This case takes KPCLOUD Information Technology Co., Ltd. as the research object. As a data-intensive enterprise, it has accumulated a vast amount of data during its business operations. Data assets have already become an important asset of KPCLOUD and play a significant role in the enterprise&#39;s development. Moreover, KPCLOUD is the first listed company to include purchased data assets in the balance sheet and has become one of the first practitioners of including data assets in the balance sheet. The inclusion of data assets in the balance sheet is an important part of an enterprise&#39;s digital transformation and also a significant driving force for it.This case aims to help students understand the definition and types of data assets, as well as how purchased data assets are included in the balance sheet and how they can empower an enterprise&#39;s digital transformation. It guides students to learn how to confirm and measure data assets under the existing accounting standards and systems, inspires students to think about the significance of including data assets in the balance sheet, and provides references for companies to include purchased data assets in the balance sheet.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《财务会计理论与实务》、《会计学》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">数据资产的类型；数据资产的确认；数据资产的计量；数据资产入表赋能企业数字化转型</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-09</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
